---
title: Beef Koftas & Tabbouleh Couscous for Dinner with Beef Kofta & Roast Veggie Rice Bowl for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day. Make your own beef koftas, then serve them with tabbouleh couscous for dinner and with roast veggies and rice for lunch. Extra delicious!

